Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:09.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Meu eterno\Namor platônico.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.10,0:00:12.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Talvez eu me sentisse\Nmelhor se eu pudesse esquecê-lo,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}mas meus pés andavam por\Nconta própria até aquele parque.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.58,0:00:27.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1\i1}Cutucava a minha própria ferida, desejando que\Na ausência da garota me causasse dor eternamente.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.66,0:00:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Boa tarde!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.73,0:00:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Isso parece\Nser gostoso...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.04,0:00:44.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Quer comer?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.16,0:00:45.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Sim!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.12,0:00:53.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Que gostoso!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.08,0:00:56.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Você tem um\Ncheiro bom.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}É o perfume\Nda minha mãe.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.87,0:01:00.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Tem um cheiro\Nadocicado.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.67,0:01:04.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Cobertura de bergamota\Ncom recheio de chocolate!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.38,0:01:05.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}O quê?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Também não\Nentendi muito bem.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.43,0:01:15.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Posso ir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.51,0:01:17.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Ainda não!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.72,0:01:27.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Posso ir?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.40,0:01:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Pode.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.03,0:01:54.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Desculpe,\Nacordei você?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.06,0:02:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Bom dia,\Nsenhorita Shinobu.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.77,0:02:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\be1}Bom dia, Kirin.
